you at the village.

261
00:20:55,833 --> 00:20:57,916
We're going to do
some hunting for the feast.

262
00:20:58,000 --> 00:21:01,208
Take good care of our
honored guests, Akeginu.

263
00:21:01,291 --> 00:21:05,500
I will... You know me.
I aim to please.

264
00:21:07,958 --> 00:21:11,041
Hotarubi...
We must inform Tenzen.

265
00:21:11,125 --> 00:21:12,958
Yes, I understand.

266
00:21:33,333 --> 00:21:35,583
Ogen-sama is dead.

267
00:21:38,875 --> 00:21:42,583
It appears Kouga
Danjo is also dead.

268
00:21:42,666 --> 00:21:45,375
They must have
killed each other.

269
00:21:46,166 --> 00:21:48,791
That's probably
how they wanted it.

270
00:21:50,166 --> 00:21:53,875
Tenzen-sama?
I don't understand.

271
00:21:57,250 --> 00:22:00,541
That's because you are
still too young, Koshiro.

272
00:22:09,458 --> 00:22:12,041
Finally it has been broken!

273
00:22:12,875 --> 00:22:16,083
Since the Tensho Era,
the No-Hostilies Pact has

274
00:22:16,166 --> 00:22:19,041
tied the hands
of the Iga and Kouga...

275
00:22:19,125 --> 00:22:22,500
But now... our hands are free.

276
00:23:55,750 --> 00:23:58,333
The No Hostilities Pact has
been broken and the race to

277
00:23:58,416 --> 00:24:01,041
finish an unsettled
score has begun.

278
00:24:01,125 --> 00:24:02,958
As the wheel of fortune turns, 

279
00:24:03,041 --> 00:24:06,958
two bloodthirsty warriors
speed down a perilous path.

280
00:24:07,041 --> 00:24:10,875
Meeting is only the
beginning of separation.

281
00:24:10,958 --> 00:24:14,000
While a spider spins
his web strand by strand,

282
00:24:14,083 --> 00:24:18,250
the smallest insect
may cause death by one bite.

283
00:24:18,333 --> 00:24:22,833
On the next Basilisk,
"The Onslaught of War."

